  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "We found Corvell on Instagram & was really impressed from the get go when Jack came to measure up to quote for some tiling in our kitchen, utility & wc - his attention to detail in checking exactly what we wanted & advising on tiles/grout etc was so useful! The quote was so competitively priced we booked on right away! Jack & Nick then did such an immaculate efficient job, we absolutely love our new tiles! Now recommending them to everyone we know and booked them to fit my mums bathroom & can’t wait to see them transform it! Thanks guys!",
      "reviewer": "Harriet",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Nick & Jack did our full bathroom renovation. They were friendly, professional, efficient, and did an exceptional job, we are thrilled with the final result. They explained everything in as much detail as possible, and set out clear expectations of what the renovation would entail. Would recommend Corvell Ltd to anyone considering having their bathroom done, they were absolutely brilliant! Thank you both so much!",
      "reviewer": "Chris",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Jack and Nick came around in August  to quote which was competitive. September the bathroom  was installed to a very high standard. Corvell came to us through recommendations which is best the form of advertising. If  anyone would like to contact me by all means don't hesitate.",
      "reviewer": "Stephen",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "We have been working very closely with Corvell LTD since the day they started and it has been nothing short of excellence. From time keeping, quality and reliability they have been a breath of fresh air. 100% recommended.",
      "reviewer": "joe",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Nick and Jack did a great job fitting a macerator toilet, where there was no existing plumbing. Really pleased with the workmanship and would highly recommend them and will use them in the future.",
      "reviewer": "Robert",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
